Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}and I’m alright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.05,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}yeah I hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.31,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I care about you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:13.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:25.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが　どうして　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:31.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて　会いたいよなんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:37.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　今日だけは思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:43.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だからあなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:48.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.03,0:23:52.24,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere yah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.49,0:23:57.62,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:57.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.91,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:00.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:03.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:12.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:19.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.01,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我还好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.05,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.01,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我听到了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.31,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:01.69,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}轻风在长发间嬉戏着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}这一切都有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.28,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}包括那些驻足不前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:13.37,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}到如今我也终于能理解并追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果不是这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:25.09,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那么这么多看不到的事物 又如何满溢出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:31.34,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少 我不会说出想见到你这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:37.01,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我说 只有今天让我追忆你可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:43.06,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以 如果我们能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:48.99,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一定不再会迷茫 而是选择当下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.78,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.03,0:23:52.24,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:57.62,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我都会为你欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.49,0:23:57.62,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:00.62,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}每当合上双眼 总是
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.91,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:03.46,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算没有绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.42,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也总能够传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.63,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算落泪也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:12.93,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为黎明一定会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:19.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会为你的归来轻声歌唱着我们摇篮曲
